reviewText: The author of this great production is very caring towards children. She loves her animals of which several of them have been rescued, creating a great production for a young audience teaching them manners, safety and other traits that will last a lifetime.

I met the director / owner / producer at a motorcycle rally in Baker City. Terri is a great person and puts her heart into these videos.
She loves teaching children all ages. My niece has watched these videos non stop. I think she wore the dvds out.
